    "en": {
      "title": "Balagiri fault for petrol ship?",
      "body_lines": [
        "The ship carrying 40,000 metric tons of octane 92 petrol did not reach Sri Lanka until this afternoon (24), a spokesman for the Ministry of Power and Energy said.",
        "When inquired about the ship, a spokesman for the Ministry of Energy further stated that 'the ship has not arrived yet'.",
        "The Minister of Power and Energy Kanchana Wijesekera stated yesterday (23) that the ship would arrive in Sri Lanka yesterday morning."
      ],
